deepin-herdr (0.3.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Rewrite in Rust with GPUI framework for cross-platform support.
  * Replace DTK/Qt6 + QTermWidget with GPUI Component + alacritty_terminal.
  * Cross-platform: Linux (X11/Wayland), macOS, Windows.
  * Single binary, no DTK/Qt dependency.
  * alacritty_terminal backend with true PTY and ANSI support.
  * Auto-connect to herdr client via PTY.
  * Preserved: herdr binary detection, auto server start, socket wait.

 -- re2zero <yangwu@uniontech.com>  Wed, 10 Jun 2026 17:00:00 +0800

deepin-herdr (0.2.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Bind terminal color scheme to theme: dark=Theme7, light=Theme10.
  * Fix translation context mismatch for application description.
  * Add StartupWMClass to .desktop for dock icon matching.
  * Fix stale socket detection when herdr exits abnormally.
  * Support Qt5/Qt6 dual build via QT_DIR cmake variable.
  * Clean up freopen stdout/stderr redirection.
  * Use DApplication::loadTranslator() for translation loading.

 -- re2zero <yangwu@uniontech.com>  Tue, 02 Jun 2026 15:30:00 +0800

deepin-herdr (0.1.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release.
  * DTK6/Qt6 GUI frontend for herdr terminal workspace manager.
  * Embeds herdr client in QTermWidget.
  * Auto-downloads herdr binary on first launch.

